import { Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

export const TechnicalItem = ({ label, value }) => {
   return (
      <Grid container direction="row" paddingB>
         <Grid item paddingRight="5px">
            <Typography fontFamily="Noto Sans">{label}</Typography>
         </Grid>
         <Grid item>
            <Typography fontFamily="Noto Sans">{value}</Typography>
         </Grid>
      </Grid>
   )
}
